description: This file defines a Flutter widget screen called ManagerFeedbackCenterScreen, which appears to be a UI component for a feedback center in a manager dashboard within a mobile application. It includes visual elements like a header, a list of placeholder items for feedback-related features, and custom styling. Additionally, it defines a private widget (_Item) for rendering individual list items.

classes.name: ManagerFeedbackCenterScreen
classes.description: A stateless widget representing the feedback center screen for managers, with a scaffold containing an app bar and a list view with header and placeholder items.

classes.name: _Item
classes.description: A private stateless widget used to display individual list items with an icon and text, styled with custom decorations and shadow effects.

methods.name: build
methods.description: Builds the widget tree for ManagerFeedbackCenterScreen, including layout, styling, and placeholder items.

methods.name: _Item.build
methods.description: Builds a styled container with an icon and text for each feedback list item.
